Text:
Seems like pb has problems with the swedish alphabet, so I take this in english then.

This is all episodes of the comic "Bacon & Egg" that was published in the magazine "Fantomen" beteween number 1/1985 and number 6/1986.

Then I say thank you to everyone who has downloaded my first torrent. I'll be seeding it for a couple of more days, but then it's enough. I've also uploaded the comics on my blog, so you can get them there if this torrent should die.

http://fittatillfrukost.blogspot.com/2011/04/bacon-agg.html
